Class ReplicationSourceShipper

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.replication.regionserver.ReplicationSourceShipper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RecoveredReplicationSourceShipper

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class ReplicationSourceShipper
extends Thread
    This thread reads entries from a queue and ships them. Entries are placed onto the queue by ReplicationSourceWALReaderThread
